  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "<span class=\"name name-earth\">Tainted Metal</span> is an unusually soft and porous metal, found in the wrecks of derelict freighters.<br><br>Locate derelicts with the use of an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Emergency Signal Scanner</span>, purchaseable from a Space Station <span class=\"name name-special\">Scrap Dealer</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "<span class=\"name name-earth\">污染的金属</span>是一种异常柔软的多孔金属，发现于荒废货船的残骸中。<br><br>使用从空间站<span class=\"name name-special\">废品收购者</span>处购买的<span class=\"name name-technology\">紧急信号扫描仪</span>定位荒废的货船。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-earth\">遭汙染的金屬</span>是一種異常柔軟且多孔洞的金屬，可在廢棄貨船的殘骸中找到。<br><br>使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">緊急訊號掃描器</span>找到棄船，接收器可向太空站上的<span class=\"name name-special\">廢料商人</span>購買。"
  },
  "PinObjectiveMessage": {
